metadata.name: J Dilla Anthology #1
metadata.description: The J Dilla Legacy Collection is a web3 digital collection that creates a new way to experience the musical impact of J Dilla. It includes some of the most iconic artwork, exclusive physical collector's items, and interactive music collectibles that cannot be found anywhere else. All of this will lead to an ultimate music Block Party experience in the metaverse. The collection is designed to give fans a glimpse into the life and work of one of hip-hop's most influential artists.
